<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s65a">section 65a of this title</ref> prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is from the Legislative Branch Appropriation Act, 1957, act <date date="1956-06-27">June 27, 1956</date>.</p>
</note>
